    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Maui’s legendary shapeshifting powers to free the island from the corrupt force of Cemyk, a nefarious creature from another world.<br> <br>Features:  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Lush 2D Open World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get lost in a 2D open world set on a Polynesian island featuring tropical forests, waterfalls, caves, volcanoes, and spiritual realms.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/a0e0c5bbff4781629d0f9198dc017da6.poster.avif?t=1766024583\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/a0e0c5bbff4781629d0f9198dc017da6.webm?t=1766024583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Expansive Metroidvania Map</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover a large map full of secrets and challenges, with tricky platforming and other obstacles to overcome. Conquer every corner to unlock new areas and obtain powerful abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/3e79a97247a15269eed7b1c98d8d4636.poster.avif?t=1766024583\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/3e79a97247a15269eed7b1c98d8d4636.webm?t=1766024583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Animal Transformations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Transform into wild animals big and small, each with distinct abilities to aid Maui in traversal and combat. Brave the island as a Green Sea Turtle, Happy Face Spider, a Kamehameha Butterfly, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/581fc22806250894752c5055289273c9.poster.avif?t=1766024583\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/581fc22806250894752c5055289273c9.webm?t=1766024583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Solve Environmental Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the wilds of the island with Maui’s iconic hook to deftly maneuver through the dense jungles and move earth and land to access new areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/c73833240aadffce48767f9982b14a63.poster.avif?t=1766024583\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/c73833240aadffce48767f9982b14a63.webm?t=1766024583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customizable Abilities &amp; Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Maui’s abilities and upgrades to fit a variety of distinct playstyles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/f3e4e4a7ae926175214548fe8a9e5568.poster.avif?t=1766024583\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/f3e4e4a7ae926175214548fe8a9e5568.webm?t=1766024583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Hand-Drawn Art Style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bask in the beauty of traditional 2D hand-drawn environments, characters, and animations, crafted with attention to detail, creating an immersive and eye-catching world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/ffb7e391fdc4af8ecf9ec6542e60d191.poster.avif?t=1766024583\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144750/extras/ffb7e391fdc4af8ecf9ec6542e60d191.webm?t=1766024583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
